    },
    "body": "\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## Purpose\r\nquant query input on XPU is not supported, so we need pass `None` in encoder attention path like full attention.\r\n\r\n## Test Plan\r\n```\r\nVLLM_XPU_FP8_DTYPE=e4m3 VLLM_XPU_USE_SAMPLER_KERNEL=0 VLLM_USE_V1=1 VLLM_ALLOW_LONG_MAX_MODEL_LEN=1 VLLM_WORKER_MULTIPROC_METHOD=spawn python3 -m vllm.entrypoints.openai.api_server --model BAAI/bge-reranker-large --enforce-eager --port 8000 --host 0.0.0.0 --trust-remote-code --gpu-memory-util=0.95 --no-enable-prefix-caching --max-num-batched-tokens=8192 --max-model-len=8192 --block-size 64 --quantization fp8 --runner pooling --convert classify\r\n\r\ncurl -X 'POST' \\\r\n  'http://0.0.0.0:8000/v1/rerank' \\\r\n  -H 'accept: application/json' \\\r\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\r\n  -d '{\r\n  \"model\": \"BAAI/bge-reranker-large\",\r\n  \"query\": \"What is the capital of France?\",\r\n  \"documents\": [\r\n    \"The capital of Brazil is Brasilia.\",\r\n    \"The capital of France is Paris.\",\r\n    \"Horses and cows are both animals.\",\r\n    \"The French have a rich tradition in engineering.\"\r\n  ]\r\n}'\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Test Result\r\n```\r\n{\"id\":\"score-996e54ad762c4bd1\",\"model\":\"BAAI/bge-reranker-large\",\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":77,\"total_tokens\":77},\"results\":[{\"index\":1,\"document\":{\"text\":\"The capital of France is Paris.\",\"multi_modal\":null},\"relevance_score\":0.998489260673523},{\"index\":0,\"document\":{\"text\":\"The capital of Brazil is Brasilia.\",\"multi_modal\":null},\"relevance_score\":0.3179512023925781},{\"index\":2,\"document\":{\"text\":\"Horses and cows are both animals.\",\"multi_modal\":null},\"relevance_score\":0.0030381125397980213},{\"index\":3,\"document\":{\"text\":\"The French have a rich tradition in engineering.\",\"multi_modal\":null},\"relevance_score\":0.000929356727283448}]}\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n<details>\r\n<summary> Essential Elements of an Effective PR Description Checklist </summary>\r\n\r\n- [ ] The purpose of the PR, such as \"Fix some issue (link existing issues this PR will resolve)\".\r\n- [ ] The test plan, such as providing test command.\r\n- [ ] The test results, such as pasting the results comparison before and after, or e2e results\r\n- [ ] (Optional) The necessary documentation update, such as updating `supported_models.md` and `examples` for a new model.\r\n- [ ] (Optional) Release notes update. If your change is user facing, please update the release notes draft in the [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YyVqrgX4gHTtrstbq8oWUImOyPCKSGnJ7xtTpmXzlRs/edit?tab=t.0).\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n",
